  - guid: 856b12a1-2aca-4045-80e7-8aeccffa0a32
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: ???
      <Content>k__BackingField: Hi, nice to meet you!
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: ???
      <Content>k__BackingField: Word around town is that a new girl just got implemented
        into the game.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: That must be you, then. My name's Aya! Let me welcome
        you.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: 'My job here is to represent the developer''s interests
        and onboard newcomers.

'
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: That basically means...I'm your boss around here.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Haha, just kidding! We're gonna be best friends.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Unfortunately we'll still have to talk business real
        quick first.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 278, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: adbb1244-9843-44b0-9e95-517a8918a1c4
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Remember your job description, or do you need a refresh?
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 801.5, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 0
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: 1f7103d6-8fa2-4929-9ece-edf31f3ec36f
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: In this game, pretty girls like you fight against
        big robots.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Market research has concluded that this is a very
        lucrative business.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: For our players, this spectacle is represented as
        an auto-battler on their phone app.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Which means that you'll do all the fighting while
        these lazy bums simply watch.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: 'You''ll have to put in some effort not to get crushed.
        But don''t worry, you''re not completely on your own. '
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: In fact, this is our business model. The loser staring
        at you is actually your lifeline and our source of income.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: During the fight, you can send them requests asking
        for healing, buffs and special attacks.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Which they have to pay for in cash, of course.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: You get it now? Your job is to...
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 1301.5, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: 03e94f63-c185-4c6d-976d-e015775a6b3a
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: SQUEEZE ALL THEIR MONEY OUT! Haha.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Fun, isn't it? It's also easier than it sounds. You
        don't really have to be a good fighter.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Just do well enough to survive and keep begging for
        help. They'll pay.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: In fact, make sure NOT to defeat your enemies without
        sending out some requests.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Free-to-Play users just clog our servers.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 1917.5, y: 518}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: 6fafc7e6-f187-4df7-be4a-fc268a917021
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: 'Time for your training day to start then!

'
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: You'll get two battles. Don't get defeated and make
        sure to fill up your Daily Quota.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Your co-worker Katoro is also standing over there.
        Want to get acquainted before the fight?
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: You can go say hi and introduce yourself if you like.
        Just don't get distracted.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: I have full trust in you, honey! Come talk to me
        again when you're ready.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 2496.5, y: 518}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
